\begin_layout Standard
(A-
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

I)v=
\begin_inset Formula $\overrightarrow{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Es un sistema lineal homogéneo con n ecuaciones y n incógnitas con 
\begin_inset Formula $v\neq$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\overrightarrow{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Queremos obtener las soluciones no triviales por ende pedimos que det(A-
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

I) = 0
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
en otras palabras quiero infinitas soluciones
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
Polinomio característico
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Se define polinomio característico a p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

)=det(A-
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

I)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Si p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

)=0 
\begin_inset Formula $\implies$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

es raíz de p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

) y será un 
\series bold
ava de A
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
gr(p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

))=n 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
donde gr es el grado del polinomio.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
el coeficiente principal será 1 si n es par y -1 si n es impar.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Si 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{K=C}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

)=(-1)
\begin_inset Formula $^{n}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda-\lambda_{1}$
\end_inset

)....(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda-\lambda_{n}$
\end_inset

)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{i}$
\end_inset

 es raíz de p(
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

) 1
\begin_inset Formula $\leq i\leq n$
\end_inset

 (n raíces complejas)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Si 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{K=R}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
tendré a la suma de n raíces reales
\end_layout

