\end_inset

 A.
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{v}=\overline{\lambda}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\overline{v}$
\end_inset

 , 
\begin_inset Formula $v\epsilon\mathbb{C}^{n}/$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $v\neq$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\overrightarrow{0}$
\end_inset


